In completing my position and research paper, I should be drawing on the work of other writers, this is the part when I must document their contributions. Which disciplines should I use?. APA or MLA?.           Whatever it is I must make sure that I follow these 3 rules.   1.The sources is introduced by a signal phrase that names its author.  2.The material being cited is followed by a page number in parentheses.  3.At the end of the paper, a list of works cited gives complete publishing information about the     source.           All those three rules are very useful, especially for my research paper...